cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.SD 

The paper proposes a framework for multimodal sentiment analysis and emotion recognition using convolutional neural network-based feature extraction from text and visual modalities. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories such as cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) which deals with visual modalities, cs.MM (Multimedia) which deals with multimedia analysis, cs.LG (Machine Learning) which deals with machine learning techniques used in the paper, and cs.SD (Sound) which deals with audio modalities.
